title: Markets Will Remain Range-Bound: Chiriseri
description: Rufaro Chiriseri, UK and Europe Fixed Income Head for RBC Wealth Management, says bond markets will continue to trade in a range until there is better clarity from data. She speaks to Bloomberg's Lizzy Burden on 'Daybreak Europe.' (Source: Bloomberg)
